# Frontend Environment Variables
#
# Local dev: leave VITE_API_URL unset (or empty) so requests use /api and Vite proxies to localhost:5000.
# Production (CI): set GitHub secret VITE_API_URL to your Elastic Beanstalk API base, e.g.:
#   http://your-env.eba-xxxxx.ap-south-1.elasticbeanstalk.com/api
#
# Optional — bypass proxy and call backend directly while developing:
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
